name: Kong Gateway - Request Logs - Business Analytics

adqlQueryList: SELECT count(*) AS "Total Requests" FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*static*"
SELECT distinct (XresponseStatus) AS "Total Requests", count(*) FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*static*"

SELECT concat(XrequestMethod, ".", XrequestUri), avg(XrequestSize) AS avgRequestSize FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*static*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*scripts*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*angular*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/css/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*.ico*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/jquery/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/js/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/images/*"

SELECT concat(XrequestMethod, ".", XrequestUri) AS Request, sum(XkongLatency), sum(XrequestLatency), sum(XproxyLatency) AS avgRequestSize FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*static*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*scripts*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*angular*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/css/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*.ico*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/jquery/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/js/*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*/images/*" LIMIT 4
SELECT XserviceName AS "Number of Requests", count(*) AS "Load per Service" FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*static*"

SELECT distinct (XserviceName) AS "Service Name", series(eventTimestamp, 1000000), avg(XrequestSize) AS "Request Size" FROM logs WHERE XrequestUri IS NOT NULL AND XrequestUri NOT LIKE "*public*" LIMIT 5
